#
# LINE Setup:
# 1. Go to https://developers.line.biz/
# 2. Create new channel (Messaging API)
# 3. Create LIFF App in channel settings
# 4. Set LIFF App URL to your app domain
# 5. Copy LIFF ID to NEXT_PUBLIC_LIFF_ID
# 6. Generate Channel Access Token for LINE_CHANNEL_ACCESS_TOKEN
#
# Supabase Setup (Recommended Project: Line App):
# 1. Go to https://supabase.com/
# 2. Create new project or use existing "Line App" project
# 3. Copy Project URL to NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
# 4. Get Project ID from URL: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/[PROJECT_ID]
# 5. Copy anon key to NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# 6. Copy service_role key to SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
# 7. Set up Row Level Security (RLS) for members-only access
